{"tid":40591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社:美聯儲決議將造成金融動盪","createTime":"2016-12-15T09:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T10:39:50.000Z","uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9627ee3d7cda27c25e76271372e4d558af1706dc","tid":40591,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:47:47.000Z","msg":"新華社發表評論稱，美國聯邦儲備委員會加息決議將造成新一輪金融動盪，指如果美國加快加息步伐推升美元滙率，將對全球造成混亂。<br />\n<br />\n評論提出，美聯儲加息將不可避免造成新的金融動盪，令過度仰賴外部融資、自身償債能力不足的國家形勢惡化，特別是那些新興國家。<br />\n<br />\n評論又指，因為各國利率水平不盡相同，如果美國未來加快加息步伐，強勢美元將對全球造成混亂，質疑美國經濟本身能否支撐美聯儲暗示的快速加息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1455723/%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BE%3A%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%B1%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%B0%87%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1455723%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BE%253A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2584%25B2%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%259B%25AA&d=jWODVY9xXFwp0mmthCJ0jJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=bb333a82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1455723/%E6%96%B0%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BE%3A%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%B1%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%B0%87%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA</a>"},{"pid":"8e3c3d4b391c119aeef4bec50987cee20a49424e","tid":40591,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"自爆自己既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc4c381911c8b09519d105014d874397d3c3bb1","tid":40591,"uid":16394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:06:05.000Z","msg":"做咩咁老實呀"},{"pid":"845347e8a2de066cd319668376e2881de789e725","tid":40591,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10: